23/08/2007
ALPBACH, Austria -- EU integration is the basis of all reforms and social changes in Montenegro, and accession is the strategic goal, Montenegrin Deputy Prime Minister Gordana Djurovic said on Wednesday (August 22nd) at a European Forum in Alpbach.
Djurovic added that Montenegro was close to signing the Stabilisation and Association Agreement with the EU.
Forum director Erhard Busek praised Montenegro for the progress its made since declaring independence last summer.
(MINA, RTCG - 23/08/07)
